Loops:
1. while loop
2. do while loop
3. for loop
4. foreach loop

1. while loop: It is an Entry control loop. In which condition is checked before entering the loop.
Syntax:
	initialization;
	while(condition){
		Statements;
		inc/dec;
	}
2. do while loop: It is known as Exit control loop. In which condition is checked after executing the statements once.
Syntax:
	do{
		Statements;
		inc/dec;
	}while(condition);


3. for loop:
	for(initialization; condition; inc/dec){
		Statements;
	}
